# manim-mechanics

Anchor-based mechanical elements for Manim Community Edition (2D).

## Goals
- Clean, simple "animation toolbox" (not a solver)
- Elements defined by anchors (start/end/pose references)
- Updater-driven redraw for smooth animations
- First-class LaTeX labels through Manim's `Tex` / `MathTex`

## Quick start (editable install)
```bash
pip install -e .
```

## Run the demo scene
```bash
manim -pqh src/manim_mechanics/scenes/demo_oscillator.py DemoOscillator
```
